  "detailed_description": "<strong>Take control of Gizmo, a super smart Corgi forced to solve Synchronous Puzzles.</strong> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129850/extras/0feda4e6c952a7d7f0a3a860ecee2cf6.poster.avif?t=1753558680\" width=610 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129850/extras/0feda4e6c952a7d7f0a3a860ecee2cf6.webm?t=1753558680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129850/extras/0feda4e6c952a7d7f0a3a860ecee2cf6.mp4?t=1753558680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>After becoming stranded on a tropical island with an abandoned secret research facility, Gizmo must complete complex tasks, with the help of his corgi clones, in order to be reunited with his missing owner. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129850/extras/99d4169aa3d906d21ac810b411c8f930.poster.avif?t=1753558680\" width=612 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129850/extras/99d4169aa3d906d21ac810b411c8f930.webm?t=1753558680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129850/extras/99d4169aa3d906d21ac810b411c8f930.mp4?t=1753558680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Complete more than 50 mentally challenging levels across 9 sectors in Corgi Cove! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129850/extras/34513472ec6f7027cdcd069463286ccd.poster.avif?t=1753558680\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129850/extras/34513472ec6f7027cdcd069463286ccd.webm?t=1753558680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129850/extras/34513472ec6f7027cdcd069463286ccd.mp4?t=1753558680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
